This paper proposes a new framework for imitation learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on model-free imitation learning, which is a type of reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the application of their framework in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
